  "body": "exceljs安装在前端，创建工作表，写入数据，导出Excel都正常。但是当我安装到后端，从接口返回buffer在从前端导出时，excel的内容变成了buffer\r\n1、这是在前端的导出\r\n<img width=\"532\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/assets/87509407/6f7a44dc-6500-45b7-9d48-869bb39b2d93\">\r\n<img width=\"387\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/assets/87509407/7ecce082-f2e6-4a73-8bcd-74fb390bd438\">\r\n2、同样的代码，我从后端接口返回buffer，再导出\r\n<img width=\"896\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/exceljs/exceljs/assets/87509407/3f5ea448-9982-4159-b071-140314a46fbb\">\r\n这是哪里出了问题\r\n\r\n\r\n",
